cast.overview: This documentary-drama hybrid explores the dangerous human impact of social networking, with tech experts sounding the alarm on their own creations.
cast.title: The Social Dilemma

details.biography: Hannah Vail is an actress originally from Colorado, Wyoming, and Texas. She has a background in regional theatre and now trains with film industry professionals at Anthony Meindl's Acting Workshop in Los Angeles. She began taking college classes full time at 16 years old with a focus in psychology. When she isn't working on a film set, she works as a CIT (Crisis Intervention Training) Actor with multiple police departments and Child Protective Services, where she frequently improvises scenarios as a minor in crisis to train officers and case workers how to deescalate mental health crises without the use of physical force or aggression. Hannah won the award for Best Actress from the 48 Hour Film Project for her lead role in 'Lucidity'.
details.name: Hannah Vail
